Reverse a linked list: each time take the first ring of the original chain and hook it up to the new chain. For example:

original chain:
          3 -> 4 -> 5 -> null
current new chain:
          2 -> 1 -> null
-------------------------------------          
Next stage:

original chain:
          4 -> 5 -> null
current new chain:
          3 -> 2 -> 1 -> null
